+        Note: If notification_ids is omitted, all unread notifications are marked read at once.
 
         Args:
             notification_ids: Optional list of notification IDs to mark as read. If not provided, marks all as read.
diff --git a/src/dalgo_mcp/tools/organization.py b/src/dalgo_mcp/tools/organization.py
